"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-24-paula-radcliffe-defends-decision-allow-convicted-rapist-compete-olympics-21291790\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Former British Olympian Paula Radcliffe has apologised after defending the decision to allow convicted rapist Steven van de Velde to compete at theParisOlympics and wishing him the 'best of luck'  Van de Velde will be representing Netherlands as part of the beach volleyball squad in the French capital.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9782252317844832, \"rank\": 0.02130211478798629, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paula Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paula_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999417534565572, \"rank\": 5.824993613721912e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984649274180676, \"rank\": 0.0015371116741091041, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8916791316427707, \"rank\": 0.11886831872138658, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old was sentenced to four years in prison in 2016after pleading guilty to raping a 12-year-old British girl when he was 19.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9782252317844832, \"rank\": 0.02130211478798629, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He resumed his volleyball career after serving 12 months of a four-year sentence and was named in the Netherlands' Olympic squad in June.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984649274180676, \"rank\": 0.0015371116741091041, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His inclusion has been one of the biggest talking points heading into thissummer's Gameswith Dutch officials standing by their decision to select him.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\", \"score\": 0.6869586773773817, \"rank\": 0.23890701985321505, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe, a former world champion marathon runner who represented Great Britain in four consecutive Olympic Games between 1996 and 2008, told LBC van de Velde 'may well have turned his life around' following his conviction, wishing him 'the best of luck'.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999968006437732, \"rank\": 2.873718609405132e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999962751644, \"rank\": 3.724739348922391e-09, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think that is a very dangerous line to go down given that we allow people who cheat in sport and take drugs in sport to then come back and then compete,' Radcliffe told Tonight with Andrew Marr.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Marr\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, to ban someone, as I understand it, he was 19 at the time and he's served his jail time and it's a long time to carry on paying for that mistake for the rest of your life.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He may well have turned it around and completely repented.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You certainly hope, I know that he is married now and has settled down.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think it's a tough thing to do to punish him twice and if he's managed to successfully turn his life around after being sent to prison and to qualify and to be playing sport at the highest level, then I actually wish him the best of luck.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Obviously, he will be watched during the village, if it were to be repeated now or it had been last year I would be saying a different thing.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I think the ban and the learning difference from 19 to 29 is huge.'\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe's comments were widely criticised on social media, with one X user describing them as 'shocking'.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really apologise for the way I phrased this.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The utter condemnation of the crime in my head went without saying but I should have clarified that.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead I poorly jumped to explaining why It would be great to exclude all who betray ideals but legally not possible.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to the post, Radcliffe said: 'I agree and can only apologise, that is not what I intended to say.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.6521038325961866, \"rank\": 0.5334957315531297, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I stress that it is not something that can be excused in any way.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was confused in my head and responding to the right to ban him from the Games and I do not know why I wished him luck.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Again I apologise.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not support him taking part, I was confused because I was clumsily trying to say that he can not be banned, he has served his jail time.\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ideally it would be great ban athletes that do not uphold the Olympic ideals and general human standards but legally that can not happen.\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Again, I fully apologise, I do not wish him luck in any way and do not know why I said that phrase at the end.\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 3052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't my intention.'\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Netherlands team boss Pieter van den Hoogenband explained this week 'measures' have been taken to facilitate Van de Velde's participation at the Games.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984649274180676, \"rank\": 0.0015371116741091041, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pieter van den Hoogenband\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\"}, {\"begin\": 3101, \"end\": 3126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pieter van den Hoogenband\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pieter_van_den_Hoogenband\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde will not speak to the mediaand is being housed away from the athlete's village.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Steven has been active in international sports and the beach volleyball world for a long time,' Van den Hoogenband, who won swimming gold medals at the 2000 and 2004 Olympics, told Dutch outlet NOS.\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3511, \"ti